<section class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4 ps-4 text-info">Frequently asked questions</h2>

    <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                <button
                        class="accordion-button collapsed"
                        type="button"
                        data-mdb-collapse-init
                        data-mdb-target="#flush-collapseOne"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="flush-collapseOne"
                >
                    <strong>I belong to a church somewhere else</strong>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div
                    id="flush-collapseOne"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                    aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne"
                    data-mdb-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
            >
                <div class="accordion-body text-muted">
                    Well that's no problem. It would just be a simple process of getting you over here. We ask a few questions first, evaluate that according to scripture,
                    then we make a unanimous vote on your membership, according to scripture. We accept all who do not know Christ as their saviour, and members need to be of sober and sound mind and of heart.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingTwo">
                <button
                        class="accordion-button collapsed"
                        type="button"
                        data-mdb-collapse-init
                        data-mdb-target="#flush-collapseTwo"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo"
                >
                    <strong>Membership pricing</strong>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div
                    id="flush-collapseTwo"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="flush-headingTwo"
                    data-mdb-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
            >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    Being a member does not cost anything, but in the Bible it did say to give 10% of tithings of your earnings to the church.
                    In the Old Testament, it said in likeness, "Give 10% to God of your earnings." Although God may not need 10% of your income,
                    but it is more of a test of faith and trust in Him.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
                <button
                        class="accordion-button collapsed"
                        type="button"
                        data-mdb-collapse-init
                        data-mdb-target="#flush-collapseThree"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controls="flush-collapseThree"
                >
                    <strong
                    >
                        Who do I know I am saved?
                    </strong
                    >
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div
                    id="flush-collapseThree"
                    class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                    aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree"
                    data-mdb-parent="#accordionFlushExample"
            >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    The bible points to this several times. And Jesus mentioned it as well. "Unless someone is born again, they cannot enter the kingdom of Heaven." The Pharisee was there to meet Jesus, named Nicodemus, and said,
                    "How can this be?" "I cannot reenter to mother's womb?" Jesus said again, unless you are born again spiritually, you cannot enter the kingdom of Heaven." Then Jesus, mentioning about the wind blowing every random direction
                    without expectation, He said that you do not know where and when the wind blows, so does the Spirit of God. Accept Jesus as your saviour and Lord, confess you are a sinner, and put your trust and faith Him, that's it!!!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>